high_descs: Go over to the rightmost kitchen sink and face it.
Pick up the knife that's on the counter in front of the sink.
Look up at the red microwave above the sink.
Use the knife to cut the potato that's in the microwave.
Close the microwave door, then look down at the sink.
Look back up at the microwave, open it, and put the knife in the microwave.
Look down at the sink, then look back up at the microwave.
Get a slice of potato out of the microwave.
Take a step to the left with the potato.
Put the potato in the leftmost sink and wash it, then pick it up again.
Bring the potato across the room to the white table with the tomato on it.
Put the potato on the table so that it's in front of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of clean potato on the table.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the left to face the right side of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the right side of the sink.
Take a step to the left to face the microwave.
Cut the potato in the microwave into slices.
Step back and look up to face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Step forward and look up to face the microwave.
Remove a slice of potato from the microwave.
Take a step to the left to face the left side of the sink.
Wash the potato slice in the sink and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the white table.
Place the potato slice on the white table.
anns.task_desc: To wash a slice of potato and place it on the white table.

high_descs: Go to the right sink
Pick up the knife
Go to the microwave
Cut the potato in the microwave
Close the microwave
Open the microwave and put the knife in
Close the microwave
Open the microwave and take a potato slice out
Go to the left sink
Wash the potato slice in the left sink
Go to the white table
Put the potato slice down on the table
anns.task_desc: Place a washed and cut potato slice on a table
